    • Class com.ceofyeast.stringgameengine.screeneditor.CellsMatrix

      class CellsMatrix extends JPanel implements Serializable

      • Serialized Fields

        • BORDER_THICKNESS
          int BORDER_THICKNESS
          Specifies thickness of border between cells; has a default value of 3. The "border" referred to is actually just the horizontal and vertical gap between the cells in cellsMatrix; this space is specified by BORDER_THICKNESS. Therefore, the border's color is set by changing the background color of the cellsMatrix.
        • cellsMatrixScrollPane
          JScrollPane cellsMatrixScrollPane
          Parent of cellsMatrixScrollPaneView, and allows the cellMatrix to be scrolled if it takes up more space than the window; is also the top-level parent of the cellsMatrix, and is therefore what's added/removed from the content pane.
        • cellsMatrixScrollPaneView
          JPanel cellsMatrixScrollPaneView
          Parent of the cellsMatrix, and whose sole purpose is to center the cellsMatrix inside the scroll pane; is also the view of the cellsMatrixScrollPane, as the name implies.
        • columnCount
          int columnCount
          Specifies number of columns of cells in cellsMatrix; can't be negative or zero.
        • font
          Font font
          Contains the font to be applied to the cells in the cellsMatrix.
        • fontName
          String fontName
          Specifies the name of the font to be used.
        • fontSize
          int fontSize
          Specifies the font size of the cells (text fields) in cellsMatrix; has a default value of 20.
        • rowCount
          int rowCount
          Specifies number of rows of cells in cellsMatrix; can't be negative or zero.
